(* Theorem: x IN (proper_divisors n) <=> (1 < x /\ x < n /\ x divides n) *)
(* Proof:
   Since x IN (divisors n)
     ==> x <= n /\ x divides n       by divisors_element
   Since x <= n but x <> n, x < n.
   If x = 0, x divides n ==> n = 0   by ZERO_DIVIDES
   But x <> n, so x <> 0.
